#: hugin1/hugin/GLPreviewFrame.cpp:2653 hugin1/hugin/GLPreviewFrame.cpp:2683
#: hugin1/hugin/GLPreviewFrame.cpp:2721 hugin1/hugin/PanoPanel.cpp:1055
